														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1600143">
									

<p>I'm not sure if I like this piece or not. I like the idea of someone who enjoys Halloween a lot because it's a day when they can turn into whatever they want, but the way you word it makes it seem like he's changing right in front of all these people. Along with that, I seem to be failing to understand why he doesn't just turn into other people during the rest of the year, or even just turn into a candy factory worker if he really likes candy that much. Also: the police officer bit didn't make much sense. Why do the police not like him?</p>
<p>Anyways, the premise was interesting, but I didn't like the execution as a whole. No vote.</p>

							</div>

								
					
